name: Alexa v1
description:
One of two works. Two different music, two different moods. Black and white. Not all darkness is black, not all white is light.
I continue to form my unique view of beauty, and am happy to show you Alexa as I see her.
Absolutely authentic music, was made also by me especially for this video. Be sure to check out the second piece. Collect both pieces together will give you a diptych.
If you bought the work, be sure to tweet me, I'll send you a link to the video in high quality.
